    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cord made from twisted, and sometimes rubberized, paper; used for a variety of purposes including packaging and furniture upsholstery.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
